You want it, you got to earn it.

708
00:44:16,612 --> 00:44:19,052
<i>Ay,</i> only for you, <i>amigo.</i>

709
00:44:21,932 --> 00:44:23,252
Any requests?

710
00:44:23,372 --> 00:44:27,132
You know my favorite, Héctor.

711
00:44:44,812 --> 00:44:48,052
<i>♪ Well, everyone knows Juanita</i>

712
00:44:49,932 --> 00:44:52,812
<i>♪ Her eyes each a different color</i>

713
00:44:54,812 --> 00:44:59,252
<i>♪ Her teeth stick out</i>
<i>And her chin goes in</i>

714
00:45:00,572 --> 00:45:02,772
<i>♪ And her...</i>

715
00:45:04,092 --> 00:45:07,172
<i>♪ Knuckles they drag on the floor</i>

716
00:45:07,292 --> 00:45:09,652
-Those aren't the words.
-There are children present.

717
