We call it the final death.

728
00:46:30,252 --> 00:46:32,332
Where did he go?

729
00:46:32,492 --> 00:46:33,852
No one knows.

730
00:46:34,012 --> 00:46:37,692
But I've met him.
I could remember him when I go back!

731
00:46:37,852 --> 00:46:39,412
No, it doesn't work like that, <i>chamaco.</i>

732
00:46:40,252 --> 00:46:43,172
Our memories,
they have to be passed down

733
00:46:43,252 --> 00:46:44,852
by those who knew us in life...

734
