Now give me your best <i>grito.</i>

794
00:50:12,372 --> 00:50:14,892
-My best <i>grito?</i>
-Come on, yell! Belt it out.

795
00:50:18,212 --> 00:50:21,452
Ah, it feels good.
Okay, now you.

796
00:50:26,812 --> 00:50:28,452
Oh, come on, kid.

797
00:50:39,452 --> 00:50:41,212
De la Cruzcito, you're on now!

798
00:50:41,372 --> 00:50:43,652
Miguel, look at me. Hey, look at me.

799
