You can do this.

800
00:50:45,012 --> 00:50:47,012
Grab their attention and don't let it go.

801
00:50:47,372 --> 00:50:49,532
Make them listen, <i>chamaco.</i>
You've got this.

802
00:50:49,692 --> 00:50:51,772
De la Cruzcito

