Look! It's Ernesto!

907
00:58:35,532 --> 00:58:36,532
De la Cruz!

908
00:58:37,932 --> 00:58:39,332
<i>Señor</i> de la Cruz!

909
00:58:41,612 --> 00:58:45,452
Pardon me! <i>Señor</i> de la Cruz!
<i>Señor</i> de la--

910
00:58:51,012 --> 00:58:52,412
<i>When you see</i>
<i>your moment,</i>

911
00:58:52,492 --> 00:58:54,012
<i>you mustn't let it pass you by.</i>

912
00:58:54,172 --> 00:58:55,852
<i>You must seize it.</i>

913
00:58:56,012 --> 00:58:57,972
<i>This one has a wise spirit.</i>

914
00:59:12,772 --> 00:59:14,212
<i>We're almost there, Dante.</i>

915
00:59:18,052 --> 00:59:20,692
<i>Señor</i> de la Cruz!
<i>Señor</i> de la--

